        Development Notes
        -----------------
        
        Make sure that `tox <https://tox.readthedocs.io/en/latest/>`_ completes successfully.
        
        Create a virtual environment::
        
          mkvirtualenv --python=python3.6 <VIRTUAL-ENVIRONMENT-NAME>
        
        Install ``tox``::
        
          pip install tox
        
        And run ``tox``::
        
          tox
